Terminals unused in grammar

   VOID
   ERR


Grammar

    0 $accept: start $end

    1 start: program

    2 program: globaldecls init

    3 globaldecls: globaldecls globaldecl
    4            | %empty

    5 globaldecl: vardecl
    6           | funcdecl

    7 vardecls: vardecls vardecl
    8         | %empty

    9 vardecl: type ID SCOL
   10        | type ID LSBR INTCONST RSBR SCOL

   11 funcdecl: type ID LPBR params RPBR block

   12 $@1: %empty

   13 block: LFBR $@1 vardecls stmts RFBR

   14 init: INIT block

   15 params: paramlist
   16       | %empty

   17 paramlist: paramlist COMMA param
   18          | param

   19 param: type ID
   20      | type ID LSBR RSBR

   21 stmts: stmts stmt
   22      | %empty

   23 stmt: loc ASSGN bool SCOL
   24     | IF LPBR bool RPBR stmt
   25     | IF LPBR bool RPBR stmt ELSE stmt
   26     | LOOP LPBR bool RPBR stmt
   27     | BREAK SCOL
   28     | RETURN factor SCOL
   29     | block

   30 args: arglist
   31     | %empty

   32 arglist: arglist COMMA arg
   33        | arg

   34 arg: factor

   35 type: INT
   36     | FLOAT

   37 loc: loc LSBR bool RSBR
   38    | ID
   39    | ID LPBR args RPBR

   40 bool: bool OR join
   41     | join

   42 join: join AND equality
   43     | equality

   44 equality: equality EQL rel
   45         | equality NEQ rel
   46         | rel

   47 rel: expr LES expr
   48    | expr LEQ expr
   49    | expr GEQ expr
   50    | expr GRE expr
   51    | expr

   52 expr: expr PLUS term
   53     | expr MINUS term
   54     | term

   55 term: term MUL unary
   56     | term DIV unary
   57     | unary

   58 unary: NOT unary
   59      | MINUS unary
   60      | factor

   61 factor: LPBR bool RPBR
   62       | loc
   63       | INTCONST
   64       | FLOATCONST


